{"id":"r13_seed_metaref_949","prompt":"서술 요청 (metaref): --- 11.","response":"--- 11. Scale Consciousness (SC1-15) — 100M 모델 Cell 생존 문제 (2026-03-27) 문제: ConsciousLM 100M (768d, 12L)에서 cell이 3개만 생존 (10 splits - 9 merges) → Φ=2.607 (4M v2의 Φ=4.12보다 낮음) SC2 ★ (Φ=2.381, ×1.8) — Dim-inverse merge threshold merge_threshold = 0.01 × (64 / dim) 768d → threshold=0.00083 → cell merge 거의 불가 → cell 생존율 극대화 ➜ train_models/conscious_lm.hexa, anima/core/runtime/anima_runtime.hexa에 반영 완료 SC1 (Φ=1.281, ×0.9) — Dim-scaled differentiation noise noise_scale = 0.02 × √(dim/64) 큰 모델은 더 큰 분화 noise 필요 ➜ train_models/conscious_lm.hexa, anima/core/runtime/anima_runtime.hexa에 반영 완료","source":"docs/consciousness-threshold-criteria.md","category":"metaref","weight":1.0,"hexad_module":null,"coherence_spans":1,"min_char":200,"max_char":4096}
{"id":"r13_seed_metaref_950","prompt":"서술 요청 (metaref): 12.","response":"12. Overfitting Prevention (OV1-15) — AnimaLM v5 과적합 방지 (2026-03-27) 문제: AnimaLM v5 train=5.13 vs val=6.50 (gap 1.37), overfitting alert 반복 OV13 ★ (Φ=1.970, ×1.5) — Batch size increase batch 4x 증가 → gradient noise 감소 → 일반화 개선 ➜ train_anima_lm.py default 변경 OV8 (Φ=1.321, ×1.0) — Dim swap augmentation 토큰 위치 10% swap → gradient checkpoint와 dtype 불일치 → 실패 결론: gradient checkpoint 사용 시 augmentation 주의 필요","source":"docs/consciousness-threshold-criteria.md","category":"metaref","weight":1.0,"hexad_module":null,"coherence_spans":1,"min_char":200,"max_char":4096}
