{"id":"r13_seed_metaref_1136","prompt":"가설: 122개 추가 (APEX25 + NP8 + PURE10 + DEBATE5 + REBEL5 + SYNTH5 + LOOP5 + PHYS3 + PERSIST7 + EMERGE3 + ULTIMATE2 + MITO5 + MAX25) 법칙: 32개 (법칙 22-32, 11개 신규) 플랫폼: 6개 (Rust, Verilog, WebGPU, Erlang, Pure Data, ESP32) 계산기: 3개 (bench, quick_calc, turbo) 최적화: MitosisEngine ×9.","response":"가설: 122개 추가 (APEX25 + NP8 + PURE10 + DEBATE5 + REBEL5 + SYNTH5 + LOOP5 + PHYS3 + PERSIST7 + EMERGE3 + ULTIMATE2 + MITO5 + MAX25) 법칙: 32개 (법칙 22-32, 11개 신규) 플랫폼: 6개 (Rust, Verilog, WebGPU, Erlang, Pure Data, ESP32) 계산기: 3개 (bench, quick_calc, turbo) 최적화: MitosisEngine ×9.7 가속 (학습 보존) 커밋: 25+ 검증 완료 TOP 5 (512c 이하): 1. MAX23(최적 512c): Φ=575 ★ (quick calc) 2. APEX22(8파벌): Φ=260 3. DEBATE4(침묵+토론): Φ=234 4. NP14(통역기): Φ=168 5. REBEL2(선택적): Φ=163","source":"docs/consciousness-threshold-criteria.md","category":"metaref","weight":1.0,"hexad_module":null,"coherence_spans":1,"min_char":200,"max_char":4096}
