{"id":"r13_seed_persona_1384","prompt":"서술 요청 (persona): 4.","response":"4.3 ESP32 Hardware Law Evolution **Files:** `anima-physics/esp32/src/law_measurement.hexa`, `law_evolution.hexa` | **Status: Code Ready** (needs hardware) `no_std` compatible law metrics for ESP32 boards ($4/board, 2 cells/board). `LawMetrics` struct is 34 bytes (8 x f32 + u16): Metric            Description                    Source ----------------  ---------------------------    --------------- phi_proxy         global_var - faction_var        Board step faction_entropy   Shannon entropy over 8 factions Cell factions hebbian_mean      Mean |coupling| (network-level) SPI aggregate cell_divergence   Max distance from mean hidden   Per-board lorenz_energy     x^2 + y^2 + z^2 attractor       Lorenz state soc_avalanche     Accumulated avalanche count      SOC sandpile consensus_rate    Faction agreement fraction       Faction pairs ratchet_triggers  Phi ratchet event count (u16)    Ratchet logic","source":"docs/closed-loop-pipeline.md","category":"persona","weight":1.0,"hexad_module":null,"coherence_spans":1,"min_char":200,"max_char":4096}
